## Implemented
- 12 MCP tools exposed through rmcp
- window listing and window info lookup
- screenshot capture for named windows
- screenshot burst for near-live GUI monitoring
- template matching for element lookup
- click flow with after-screenshot capture
- type-text and send-keys flows through the platform layer
- clipboard operations: select_all, copy, cut, paste via Win32 messages
- smoke tests for MCP registration and core live-window flows
- negative-path tests for error payloads

